                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1193" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM LEE</persName>
                  </hi>. I slept in the next bed to the prisoner, at the lodging in Fieid-lane—I saw him on the Wednesday morning after this in Newgate-street—he had a pair of boots on his feet—I gave information to the officer who took him.</p>
